laboratory_examinations.findings: Serum creatinine value of 2.7. Estimated GFR = 24 if non African-American (mL/min/1.73 m2); GFR = 30 if African-American (mL/min/1.73 m2). GFR<60 indicating Chronic Kidney Disease.

AP and upright supine radiographs show multiple dilated predominantly small bowel loops with multiple air-fluid levels consistent with ileus. Oral contrast is seen in small bowel loops and the cecum. No free intra-abdominal air noted.
